Compile/run:
     - Compile using
        make gerp
     - run executable with
        ./gerp inputDirectory outputFile 

*******************************************************************************

Program Purpose: 
     
     The program purpose is that, given a directory that contains a set of 
     files, build a data structure that indexes them, and using that index,
     respond to the user queries.

*******************************************************************************

Acknowledgements: 

     N/A

